{"id":"113760557884199400","created_at":"2025-01-02T20:05:56.387Z","in_reply_to_id":null,"in_reply_to_account_id":null,"sensitive":false,"spoiler_text":"","visibility":"public","language":"en","uri":"https://chaos.social/users/foosel/statuses/113760557884199400","url":"https://chaos.social/@foosel/113760557884199400","replies_count":5,"reblogs_count":1,"favourites_count":33,"quotes_count":0,"edited_at":null,"content":"\u003cp\u003eContinuing my start-of-the-year clean-up project tradition (for last year\u0026#39;s project see \u003ca href=\"https://chaos.social/@foosel/111687404140972445\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" translate=\"no\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"invisible\"\u003ehttps://\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"ellipsis\"\u003echaos.social/@foosel/111687404\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"invisible\"\u003e140972445\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/a\u003e).\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eToday I tackled the hallway shelf and the built-in closet. Filled up several garbage bags once more. Ouch, my back 😅\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eI also decided to throw out my first 3d printer that was still stored in the closet, as much as it saddens me. It\u0026#39;s no longer working \u0026amp; it\u0026#39;s taking up too much space for that. But I\u0026#39;ll keep the front plate \u0026amp; Pi 😊\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eNo before pictures for you bw - too embarrassing 😬\u003c/p\u003e","reblog":null,"application":{"name":"Tusky","website":"https://tusky.app"},"account":{"id":"235099","username":"foosel","acct":"foosel","display_name":"Gina Häußge","locked":false,"bot":false,"discoverable":true,"indexable":true,"group":false,"created_at":"2020-01-01T00:00:00.000Z","note":"\u003cp\u003e🐒 Passionate code monkey 👩‍💻 Geek 🎮 Gamer 🧗‍♀️ Bouldering apprentice 💡 Problem solver 🐍 Python wrangler 🐙 Creator \u0026amp; Maintainer of OctoPrint\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eAdmin of plushies.social \u0026amp; one half of \u003cspan class=\"h-card\" translate=\"no\"\u003e\u003ca href=\"http